\n6《杜氏家谱》，元代刻本1册，（元）佚名纂修，山西图书馆藏\n\n7.《杨村杜氏家谱》，不分卷，一册，（民国）杜涵修，民国三十二年铅印本，山西馆藏\n\n\n\n8.《马庄杜氏宗谱》十二卷十二册，（清）杜绍彩等修，宣统三年振德堂刻本，山西馆藏\n\n\n\n9.《少陵新谱》（又名《杜甫家系》)，一册，〈民国李春坪修，民国二十四年铅印本，山西馆藏\n\n\n\n10.《杜氏家谱》三卷，线装，杜鸿年编，天津图书馆藏11.《咸平邸阁杜氏集祖茔家谱》清嘉庆八年修\n\n12.《冀镇杜氏族谱》，四卷，（清）杜继瑗、杜世永纂，清同治七年（1868）刻本，二册。中国人民大学图书馆藏\n\n\n\n13.《杜氏家谱》，两卷，清代杜受全修14.《宿神王室族谱》(杜氏)15.《杜氏世谱》，清宣统辛亥年辑16.《太平杜氏重修家谱》，杜子质修\n\n## 渑池杜氏宗谱\n\n三三八", "isStart": false, "isEnd": true, "images": {}}, "outputImages": {"layout_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//bf116ce9-ba89-4fb0-90ff-8146799c7302/layout_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A28%3A42Z%2F-1%2F%2F320fe2a2350a244539d8261a6a54c390c2dce8cc92d75f113dee8604bbdf161f", "region_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//bf116ce9-ba89-4fb0-90ff-8146799c7302/region_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A28%3A43Z%2F-1%2F%2Fd016b9f337947042a572d38f557cb51c869a2fd755d743e8bab58c8be5492bae", "overall_ocr_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//bf116ce9-ba89-4fb0-90ff-8146799c7302/overall_ocr_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A28%3A43Z%2F-1%2F%2Fe123f397d2311897ea3094d9f25c667aabedaefebb8f3702b1bc16208f9d2eec", "layout_order_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//bf116ce9-ba89-4fb0-90ff-8146799c7302/layout_order_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A28%3A43Z%2F-1%2F%2F0343bf720363398406c608c230a2f57536a3f980e43e531870176805b64f20c4"}, "inputImage": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//bf116ce9-ba89-4fb0-90ff-8146799c7302/input_img_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A28%3A42Z%2F-1%2F%2F90ee14ee1f7d382